cienaCesMcastFilterMIB.name: cienaCesMcastFilterMIB

revisions.description: Added objects cienaCesMcastIgmpQueryEngineOperState, cienaCesMcastRouterOlderVersionQuerierTimeRemaining, cienaCesMcastRouterQueryIntervalTimeRemaining, cienaCesMcastGlobalSnoopAdminState. Clarified DESCRIPTION of cienaCesMcastGlobalSnoopState. Defined an object-identifier cienaCesMcastGlobalResources and twelve objects under it for reporting global resource information.

cienaCesMcastFilterMIB.contactinfo: Mib Meister 115 North Sullivan Road Spokane Valley, WA 99037 USA Phone: +1 509 242 9000 Email: support@ciena.com
cienaCesMcastFilterMIB.description: This module defines the IGMP Multicast SNMP objects.

InterfaceType.name: InterfaceType
InterfaceType.description: Interface type of a multicast member or router interface.

cienaCesMcastGlobalAdminState.name: cienaCesMcastGlobalAdminState
cienaCesMcastGlobalAdminState.description: This object represents global multicast admin state.

cienaCesMcastFilterServiceTable.name: cienaCesMcastFilterServiceTable
cienaCesMcastFilterServiceTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing multicast service configuration on the L2FDs (Layer 2 forwarding domains - VS/VLAN).

cienaCesMcastFilterServiceEntry.name: cienaCesMcastFilterServiceEntry
cienaCesMcastFilterServiceEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the cienaCesMcastFilterActivationTable.

cienaCesMcastFilterServiceType.name: cienaCesMcastFilterServiceType
cienaCesMcastFilterServiceType.description: The service instance type on which this multicast filter is configured.

cienaCesMcastFilterServiceIndex.name: cienaCesMcastFilterServiceIndex
cienaCesMcastFilterServiceIndex.description: The service instance index on which this multicast filter is configured.

cienaCesMcastFilterServiceAdminState.name: cienaCesMcastFilterServiceAdminState
cienaCesMcastFilterServiceAdminState.description: This object represents the admin state of multicast-services the given service Instance.

cienaCesMcastFilterServiceOperState.name: cienaCesMcastFilterServiceOperState
cienaCesMcastFilterServiceOperState.description: This object represents the operational state of multicast-services on the given service Instance.

cienaCesMcastFilterServiceUMFState.name: cienaCesMcastFilterServiceUMFState
cienaCesMcastFilterServiceUMFState.description: This object represents how unknown multicast frames are handled for this multicast service. 'flood' indicates that the device will flood all the unresolved messages for this service instance to all the interfaces in the flooding domain. 'drop' causes the device to drop all the unresolved messages for this service.

cienaCesMcastFilterServerInterfaceTable.name: cienaCesMcastFilterServerInterfaceTable
cienaCesMcastFilterServerInterfaceTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing the authorized server ports.

cienaCesMcastFilterServerInterfaceEntry.name: cienaCesMcastFilterServerInterfaceEntry
cienaCesMcastFilterServerInterfaceEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the cienaCesMcastFilterServerInterfaceTable.

cienaCesMcastFilterServerInterfaceType.name: cienaCesMcastFilterServerInterfaceType
cienaCesMcastFilterServerInterfaceType.description: Interface type of server interface from which the IGMP query messages can be received, and joins/leaves messages can be sent.

cienaCesMcastFilterServerInterfaceIndex.name: cienaCesMcastFilterServerInterfaceIndex
cienaCesMcastFilterServerInterfaceIndex.description: Interface Id of the server interface from which the IGMP query messages can be received, and joins/leaves messages can be sent.

cienaCesMcastFilterServerInterfaceLiType.name: cienaCesMcastFilterServerInterfaceLiType
cienaCesMcastFilterServerInterfaceLiType.description: This object has the same definition as cienaCesMcastFilterServerInterfaceType.

cienaCesMcastFilterServerInterfaceLiInde.name: cienaCesMcastFilterServerInterfaceLiIndex
cienaCesMcastFilterServerInterfaceLiInde.description: This object has the same definition as cienaCesMcastFilterServerInterfaceIndex.

cienaCesMcastGlobalSnoopState.name: cienaCesMcastGlobalSnoopState
cienaCesMcastGlobalSnoopState.description: This object represents global IGMP Snooping operational state.

cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopTable.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopTable
cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing the configuration parameters for the IGMP snooping.

cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopEntry.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopEntry
cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopTable.

cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopEnable.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopEnable
cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopEnable.description: This object represents admin state of IGMP snooping for a multicast service.

cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopRobustness.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopRobustness
cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopRobustness.description: The number of replies to send for each multicast group.

cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopProxyQueryInterval.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopProxyQueryInterval
cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopProxyQueryInterval.description: The interval period between each general query sent to the router. This parameter specifies how often to repeat the group specific query. Default value is 125 seconds. Note that the actual rate may be slower when the switch becomes busy, so this parameter should be thought of as a minimum time interval.

cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopProxyQueryReplyTmo.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopProxyQueryReplyTmo
cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopProxyQueryReplyTmo.description: The amount of time to receive a membership report after a query message is sent. This value goes directly into the query packet.

cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopProxyQueryDelay.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopProxyQueryDelay
cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopProxyQueryDelay.description: The amount of time to wait before sending the next group specific query downstream. General queries are sent one interface at a time.

cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopLingerTmo.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopLingerTmo
cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopLingerTmo.description: This value specifies the amount of time that a multicast filter is in place after the last host has left. In essence it configures how long to filter the stream after all the hosts have left the group. This can tune the system as to how long the router has to remove the stream from the subnet. The minimum value is 1 second, with no maximum value.

cienaCesMcastIgmpQueryEngineState.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpQueryEngineState
cienaCesMcastIgmpQueryEngineState.description: This object represents query engine state for a given multicast service.

cienaCesMcastIgmpProxyQuerySrcIpAddrType.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpProxyQuerySrcIpAddrType
cienaCesMcastIgmpProxyQuerySrcIpAddrType.description: This object represents the source IP address type for the multicast service.

cienaCesMcastIgmpProxyQuerySrcIpAddr.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpProxyQuerySrcIpAddr
cienaCesMcastIgmpProxyQuerySrcIpAddr.description: This object represents the source IP address for the multicast service.

cienaCesMcastIgmpRouterQueryInterval.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpRouterQueryInterval
cienaCesMcastIgmpRouterQueryInterval.description: This object represents the router query interval for the given multicast service.

cienaCesMcastIgmpMinResponseTime.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpMinResponseTime
cienaCesMcastIgmpMinResponseTime.description: This object represents the minimum response time for the given multicast service.

cienaCesMcastIgmpDefaultRouterInterfaceT.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpDefaultRouterInterfaceType
cienaCesMcastIgmpDefaultRouterInterfaceT.description: This object represents the default router interface type for the given multicast service.

cienaCesMcastIgmpDefaultRouterInterfaceI.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpDefaultRouterInterfaceId
cienaCesMcastIgmpDefaultRouterInterfaceI.description: This object represents the default router interface id for the given multicast service.

cienaCesMcastIgmpInquisitiveLeaveState.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpInquisitiveLeaveState
cienaCesMcastIgmpInquisitiveLeaveState.description: This object represents the IGMP inquisitive leave state for the given multicast service.

cienaCesMcastIgmpLastMemberQueryInterval.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpLastMemberQueryInterval
cienaCesMcastIgmpLastMemberQueryInterval.description: This object represents the last membership query interval for the given multicast service.

cienaCesMcastIgmpPriority.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpPriority
cienaCesMcastIgmpPriority.description: This object represents the priority of IGMP packets for this multicast service.

cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopRouterRangeStartIp.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopRouterRangeStartIpAddrType
cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopRouterRangeStartIp.description: The IP address type of first IP Address of the router IP Address range.

cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopRouterRangeStartIp.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopRouterRangeStartIpAddr
cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopRouterRangeStartIp.description: The first IP Address of the router IP Address range.

cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopRouterRangeEndIpAd.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopRouterRangeEndIpAddrType
cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopRouterRangeEndIpAd.description: The IP address type of the last IP Address of the router IP Address range.

cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopRouterRangeEndIpAd.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopRouterRangeEndIpAddr
cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopRouterRangeEndIpAd.description: The last IP Address of the router IP Address range. When range is undefined, all leave/join messages are forwarded to the router even when the multicast stream does not originate from the router. If the range is defined, leave/join messages are filtered. The default value for this object is equal to the value of cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopRouterRangeStartIpAddr.

cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopActiveLingerTimeou.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopActiveLingerTimeout
cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopActiveLingerTimeou.description: This object specifies the active linger timeout in seconds.

cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopServerTopology.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopServerTopology
cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopServerTopology.description: This object specifies the server topology.

cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopRapidRecoveryMode.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopRapidRecoveryMode
cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopRapidRecoveryMode.description: Specifies whether the rapid recovery mode is set to on or off. If this object is set to ON then the device generates and accepts query packets with source IP = 0 else in the OFF state, it does not.

cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopQuerierCompatibili.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopQuerierCompatibilityMode
cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopQuerierCompatibili.description: This object specifies the query engine compatibility mode.

cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopForkMode.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopForkMode
cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopForkMode.description: This object specifies whether IGMP Forking mode is set to on or off.

cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopEnableOperState.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopEnableOperState
cienaCesMcastIgmpSnoopEnableOperState.description: This object represents the operational state of IGMP snooping on the given multicast service

cienaCesMcastRouterInterfaceType.name: cienaCesMcastRouterInterfaceType
cienaCesMcastRouterInterfaceType.description: Specifies the interface type for the interface from where router queries are coming.

cienaCesMcastRouterInterfaceId.name: cienaCesMcastRouterInterfaceId
cienaCesMcastRouterInterfaceId.description: Specifies the interface Id of the interface from where router queries are coming.

cienaCesMcastReportSendInterfaceType.name: cienaCesMcastReportSendInterfaceType
cienaCesMcastReportSendInterfaceType.description: The obejct specifies the interface type of the interface where IGMP reports are sent. Not always the same as the router interface.

cienaCesMcastReportSendInterfaceId.name: cienaCesMcastReportSendInterfaceId
cienaCesMcastReportSendInterfaceId.description: The obejct specifies the interface id of the interface where IGMP reports are sent. Not always the same as the router interface.

cienaCesMcastRouterCompatibilityMode.name: cienaCesMcastRouterCompatibilityMode
cienaCesMcastRouterCompatibilityMode.description: This object specifies the IGMP version of the router.

cienaCesMcastReportSendInterfaceIsMeshVc.name: cienaCesMcastReportSendInterfaceIsMeshVc
cienaCesMcastReportSendInterfaceIsMeshVc.description: Specifies whether the current report send interface is a meshvc or not.

cienaCesMcastIgmpQueryEngineOperState.name: cienaCesMcastIgmpQueryEngineOperState
cienaCesMcastIgmpQueryEngineOperState.description: This object represents query engine operational state for a given multicast service. Active when query-engine is enabled and active, inactive when query-engine is enabled and not active, disabled otherwise.

cienaCesMcastRouterOlderVersionQuerierTi.name: cienaCesMcastRouterOlderVersionQuerierTimeRemaining
cienaCesMcastRouterOlderVersionQuerierTi.description: This object specifies the older version querier time remaining in seconds. This is only applicable when an external IGMP querier is present and an older version query is heard.

cienaCesMcastRouterQueryIntervalTimeRema.name: cienaCesMcastRouterQueryIntervalTimeRemaining
cienaCesMcastRouterQueryIntervalTimeRema.description: This object specifies the query interval time remaining in seconds. This timer will not be applicable if value for object cienaCesMcastIgmpQueryEngineOperState is active.

cienaCesMcastChannelStreamTable.name: cienaCesMcastChannelStreamTable
cienaCesMcastChannelStreamTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing the configuration parameters for the multicast channel stream.

cienaCesMcastChannelStreamEntry.name: cienaCesMcastChannelStreamEntry
cienaCesMcastChannelStreamEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the cienaCesMcastChannelStreamTable.

cienaCesMcastChanelStreamStartGroupAddrT.name: cienaCesMcastChanelStreamStartGroupAddrType
cienaCesMcastChanelStreamStartGroupAddrT.description: The Inet address type of first IP Address of the multicast IP Address range.

cienaCesMcastChanelStreamStartGroupAddr.name: cienaCesMcastChanelStreamStartGroupAddr
cienaCesMcastChanelStreamStartGroupAddr.description: The first IP Address of the multicast IP Address range.

cienaCesMcastChanelStreamStartGroupAddrP.name: cienaCesMcastChanelStreamStartGroupAddrPrefixLen
cienaCesMcastChanelStreamStartGroupAddrP.description: The prefix lenngth of first IP Address of the multicast IP Address range.

cienaCesMcastChanelStreamEndGroupAddrTyp.name: cienaCesMcastChanelStreamEndGroupAddrType
cienaCesMcastChanelStreamEndGroupAddrTyp.description: The Inet Address type of last IP Address of the multicast IP address range.

cienaCesMcastChanelStreamEndGroupAddr.name: cienaCesMcastChanelStreamEndGroupAddr
cienaCesMcastChanelStreamEndGroupAddr.description: The last IP Address of the multicast IP address range.

cienaCesMcastChannelStreamExIfcMemTable.name: cienaCesMcastChannelStreamExIfcMemTable
cienaCesMcastChannelStreamExIfcMemTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing the excluded interface list per multicast service for channel stream.

cienaCesMcastChannelStreamExIfcMemEntry.name: cienaCesMcastChannelStreamExIfcMemEntry
cienaCesMcastChannelStreamExIfcMemEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the cienaCesMcastChannelStreamExIfcMemTable.

cienaCesMcastChannelStreamExIfcType.name: cienaCesMcastChannelStreamExIfcType
cienaCesMcastChannelStreamExIfcType.description: The Interface type of the interface to be excluded from channel stream.

cienaCesMcastChannelStreamExIfcIndex.name: cienaCesMcastChannelStreamExIfcIndex
cienaCesMcastChannelStreamExIfcIndex.description: The Interface Id of the interface to be excluded from channel stream.

cienaCesMcastChannelStreamExIfcLiType.name: cienaCesMcastChannelStreamExIfcLiType
cienaCesMcastChannelStreamExIfcLiType.description: The Interface type of the interface to be excluded from channel stream.

cienaCesMcastChannelStreamExIfcLiIndex.name: cienaCesMcastChannelStreamExIfcLiIndex
cienaCesMcastChannelStreamExIfcLiIndex.description: The Interface Id of the interface to be excluded from channel stream.

cienaCesMcastGlobalSnoopAdminState.name: cienaCesMcastGlobalSnoopAdminState
cienaCesMcastGlobalSnoopAdminState.description: This object represents global IGMP Snooping administratively configured state.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupTable.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupTable
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing all the multicast groups.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupEntry.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupEntry
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the cienaCesMcastFilterGroupTable.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupAddrType.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupAddrType
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupAddrType.description: The inet address type of multicast group IP address.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupAddrPrefixLen.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupAddrPrefixLen
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupAddrPrefixLen.description: The prefix length of multicast group IP address.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupState.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupState
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupState.description: The current state of the multicast stream.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupType.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupType
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupType.description: The type of the multicast stream.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSource.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSource
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSource.description: The source for this multicast stream.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberCount.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberCount
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberCount.description: The number of member interfaces that joined the group.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupCompatibilityMod.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupCompatibilityMode
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupCompatibilityMod.description: The group compatibility mode for this group based on the lowest version of IGMP membership reports recieved for this multicast stream.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupIGMPV1HostPresen.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupIGMPV1HostPresentTimeRemainingValue
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupIGMPV1HostPresen.description: The remaining time for IGMPV1 host present timer value for this multicast stream.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupIGMPV2HostPresen.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupIGMPV2HostPresentTimeRemainingValue
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupIGMPV2HostPresen.description: The remaining time for IGMPV2 host present timer value for this multicast stream.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupFilterMode.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupFilterMode
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupFilterMode.description: The src address filter mode for this multicast stream.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupNumOfSrcAddrs.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupNumOfSrcAddrs
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupNumOfSrcAddrs.description: The number of source addresses for this multicast stream.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupTimer.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupTimer
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupTimer.description: The group timer value for this multicast stream.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSrcRecordTable.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSrcRecordTable
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSrcRecordTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing all the source address records of the multicast groups.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSrcRecordEntry.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSrcRecordEntry
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSrcRecordEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberTable.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSrcRecordSrcIpAd.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSrcRecordSrcIpAddrType
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSrcRecordSrcIpAd.description: The Inet address type of IP address of the source record table for the multicast group

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSrcRecordSrcIp.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSrcRecordSrcIp
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSrcRecordSrcIp.description: The IP address of the source record table for the multicast group

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSrcRecordSrcIpAd.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSrcRecordSrcIpAddrPrefixLen
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSrcRecordSrcIpAd.description: The inet address prefix length of IP address of the source record table for the multicast group

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSrcRecordSrcIpAd.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSrcRecordSrcIpAddress
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSrcRecordSrcIpAd.description: The IP address of the source record table for the multicast group. The mode of this source address is determined by the group filter mode - cienaCesMcastFilterGroupFilterMode object.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSrcRecordSrcTime.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSrcRecordSrcTimer
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupSrcRecordSrcTime.description: The remaining source timer value of the source address.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberTable.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberTable
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing all the interface members of the multicast groups.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberEntry.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberEntry
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberTable.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberInterfaceT.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberInterfaceType
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberInterfaceT.description: The interface type of the group member

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberInterfaceI.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberInterfaceIndex
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberInterfaceI.description: The interface Id of the group member.

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberInterfaceL.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberInterfaceLiType
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberInterfaceL.description: The interface type of the group member

cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberInterfaceL.name: cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberInterfaceLiIndex
cienaCesMcastFilterGroupMemberInterfaceL.description: The interface Id of the group member.

cienaCesMcastMaxServiceInstances.name: cienaCesMcastMaxServiceInstances
cienaCesMcastMaxServiceInstances.description: This object represents maximum number of IGMP service instances supported.

cienaCesMcastCurrentServiceInstances.name: cienaCesMcastCurrentServiceInstances
cienaCesMcastCurrentServiceInstances.description: This object represents the current number of IGMP service instances configured.

cienaCesMcastMaxMcastGroups.name: cienaCesMcastMaxMcastGroups
cienaCesMcastMaxMcastGroups.description: This object represents the maximum number of multicast groups supported.

cienaCesMcastCurrentMcastGroups.name: cienaCesMcastCurrentMcastGroups
cienaCesMcastCurrentMcastGroups.description: This object represents the current number of multicast groups.

cienaCesMcastMaxSrcAddrRecords.name: cienaCesMcastMaxSrcAddrRecords
cienaCesMcastMaxSrcAddrRecords.description: This object represents the maximum number of multicast source address records.

cienaCesMcastCurrentSrcAddrRecords.name: cienaCesMcastCurrentSrcAddrRecords
cienaCesMcastCurrentSrcAddrRecords.description: This object represents the current number of source address records.

cienaCesMcastMaxTimers.name: cienaCesMcastMaxTimers
cienaCesMcastMaxTimers.description: This object represents the maximum number of multicast timers.

cienaCesMcastCurrentTimers.name: cienaCesMcastCurrentTimers
cienaCesMcastCurrentTimers.description: This object represents the current number of multicast timers.

cienaCesMcastMaxLogicalInterfaces.name: cienaCesMcastMaxLogicalInterfaces
cienaCesMcastMaxLogicalInterfaces.description: This object represents the maximum number of Logical Interfaces.

cienaCesMcastCurrentLogicalInterfaces.name: cienaCesMcastCurrentLogicalInterfaces
cienaCesMcastCurrentLogicalInterfaces.description: This object represents the current number of Logical Interfaces.

cienaCesMcastMaxGrpMemberInterfaces.name: cienaCesMcastMaxGrpMemberInterfaces
cienaCesMcastMaxGrpMemberInterfaces.description: This object represents the maximum number of Group member Interfaces.

cienaCesMcastCurrentGrpMemberInterfaces.name: cienaCesMcastCurrentGrpMemberInterfaces
cienaCesMcastCurrentGrpMemberInterfaces.description: This object represents the current number of Group member Interfaces.

cienaCesMcastFilterStatsTable.name: cienaCesMcastFilterStatsTable
cienaCesMcastFilterStatsTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing the multicast statistics.

cienaCesMcastFilterStatsEntry.name: cienaCesMcastFilterStatsEntry
cienaCesMcastFilterStatsEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the cienaCesMcastFilterServerTable.

cienaCesMcastStaticGrpCount.name: cienaCesMcastStaticGrpCount
cienaCesMcastStaticGrpCount.description: The total number of static multicast groups.

cienaCesMcastDynamicGrpCount.name: cienaCesMcastDynamicGrpCount
cienaCesMcastDynamicGrpCount.description: The total number of dynamic mcast groups.

cienaCesMcastJoinMessagesRx.name: cienaCesMcastJoinMessagesRx
cienaCesMcastJoinMessagesRx.description: The total number of join messages received.

cienaCesMcastLeaveMessagesRx.name: cienaCesMcastLeaveMessagesRx
cienaCesMcastLeaveMessagesRx.description: The total number of leave messages received.

cienaCesMcastV3ReportsRx.name: cienaCesMcastV3ReportsRx
cienaCesMcastV3ReportsRx.description: The total number of V3 membership reports recieved.

cienaCesMcastQueryMessagesRx.name: cienaCesMcastQueryMessagesRx
cienaCesMcastQueryMessagesRx.description: The total number of queries received.

cienaCesMcastQueryRxDiscards.name: cienaCesMcastQueryRxDiscards
cienaCesMcastQueryRxDiscards.description: The total number of queries discarded.

cienaCesMcastQueryTimeouts.name: cienaCesMcastQueryTimeouts
cienaCesMcastQueryTimeouts.description: The total number of timeouts waiting for the router to send query.

cienaCesMcastUnknownPktTypeRx.name: cienaCesMcastUnknownPktTypeRx
cienaCesMcastUnknownPktTypeRx.description: The total number of unknown (unknown type ) IGMP packets received.

cienaCesMcastRouterRxDiscards.name: cienaCesMcastRouterRxDiscards
cienaCesMcastRouterRxDiscards.description: The total number of messages discarded by the router. This happens when join comes in from a router interface.

cienaCesMcastHostRxDiscards.name: cienaCesMcastHostRxDiscards
cienaCesMcastHostRxDiscards.description: The total number of messages discarded by the host. This happens when a join/leave comes in from a interface, but no router interface is established.

cienaCesMcastBadChecksumRx.name: cienaCesMcastBadChecksumRx
cienaCesMcastBadChecksumRx.description: The total number of packets received with bad IP checksum.

cienaCesMcastL2L3MismatchRx.name: cienaCesMcastL2L3MismatchRx
cienaCesMcastL2L3MismatchRx.description: The total number of IGMP Layer2 / Layer 3 mismatch packets received.

cienaCesMcastTotalMembers.name: cienaCesMcastTotalMembers
cienaCesMcastTotalMembers.description: The total number of group members for all groups in the given multicast service.

cienaCesMcastLingerCount.name: cienaCesMcastLingerCount
cienaCesMcastLingerCount.description: The total number of groups in linger state.
